00:04:45.830 --> 00:04:47.270
Keep them safe.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.950
Don't let them be separated again.

00:04:48.950 --> 00:04:49.920
Got it?

00:04:50.950 --> 00:04:52.240
Understood, Mother.

