00:19:16.750 --> 00:19:17.480
Smells good?

00:19:17.880 --> 00:19:18.640
Tastes good?

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:23.480
It's so good.

00:19:24.590 --> 00:19:25.450
Take your time.

00:19:29.880 --> 00:19:30.610
Give me a hug.

00:19:37.160 --> 00:19:38.090
Enjoy your meal.

00:19:38.630 --> 00:19:40.110
If you want more, just tell me.

00:19:40.110 --> 00:19:42.370
