00:21:19.290 --> 00:21:20.610
who fears nothing,

00:21:20.640 --> 00:21:21.590
to take the fall.

00:21:21.680 --> 00:21:22.510
How vicious.

00:21:24.440 --> 00:21:25.400
Your Li family

00:21:25.720 --> 00:21:27.580
also wants a foothold in Nanjing?

00:21:27.690 --> 00:21:28.290
